author: johnh
msg: Factoring out transports from rpc.js into separate "classes."

As described in http://shindig-dev.markmail.org/search/?q=rpc.js#query:rpc.js+page:1+mid:uvfylmfbjc362nsm+state:results, this is prerequisite work for fixing some long-standing rpc.js shortcomings (eg some transports drop messages sent before they're set up fully) and optimizations (User-Agent-based emitting of transport code for code size optimization).
* FF 2 w/ setup hack forcing IFPC (forceParentVerifiable()) (IFPC)
